{"tid":2391744,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[眼鏡撚入] 帶眼鏡既你, 會去眼鏡舖到調教眼鏡, 定自己調教","createTime":"2021-02-02T11:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T12:56:48.000Z","uid":24061,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"29c70126a0d93242df73da0aa3189fb22e1cc42d","tid":2391744,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"係咁既,<br />\n小弟就好深近視, 帶眼鏡通常係新黑到買鏡框<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 新黑既眼鏡雖然靚, 但就比較重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, <br />\n好多時成日帶眼鏡帶得耐個鏡框就會愈帶愈闊, 好容易就sir落黎, (通常一個月度)<br />\n搵眼鏡舖職員較, 有時又未必調教得好, 有時會較到好緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 又要辛苦一星期待佢慢慢鬆番, 但一過多幾星期後就又要再搵佢地教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過自己教, 教到爛左副眼鏡, 就有陰影唔敢再自己較, 因為深近視副副眼鏡都好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問下咁多位巴打, <br />\n通常自己眼鏡帶耐左鬆左會去眼鏡舖度搵職員幫你調教,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定自己調教?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇教眼鏡既高手可以入黎教下我地點樣自己教眼鏡係最好。<br />\n<br />\n覺我長遠都係自己較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c6cc434d083baca8a892daa578e8846721247d","tid":2391744,"uid":140140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"比佢教啦又唔駛錢"},{"pid":"7262e8e8d3a28bc158d9b31db4e79cea9d06e0f1","tid":2391744,"uid":24061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6c6cc434d083baca8a892daa578e8846721247d","tid":2391744,"uid":140140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"比佢教啦又唔駛錢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"有時佢較得唔係我想要既效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為深近視, 個鏡片好重, 好易sir落黎, 叫佢教番緊, 有時又太緊"},{"pid":"b8ff3eddb7668a7d34fe72dc0bcb3693f2db0892","tid":2391744,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7262e8e8d3a28bc158d9b31db4e79cea9d06e0f1","tid":2391744,"uid":24061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6c6cc434d083baca8a892daa578e8846721247d","tid":2391744,"uid":140140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"比佢教啦又唔駛錢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"有時佢較得唔係我想要既效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為深近視, 個鏡片好重, 好易sir落黎, 叫佢教番緊, 有時又太緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e4b21980a01423da49595b000d187146a74898","tid":2391744,"uid":184787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:40:03.000Z","msg":"好難答你啵<br />\n如果條邊位咪自己屈下佢睇下搞唔搞得掂<br />\n鼻托啲位就會就下力試下，但唔敢太大力，斷左就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087db89c32daf4fd89465e032a1ca2649766dc3b","tid":2391744,"uid":184787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7262e8e8d3a28bc158d9b31db4e79cea9d06e0f1","tid":2391744,"uid":24061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6c6cc434d083baca8a892daa578e8846721247d","tid":2391744,"uid":140140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"比佢教啦又唔駛錢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"有時佢較得唔係我想要既效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為深近視, 個鏡片好重, 好易sir落黎, 叫佢教番緊, 有時又太緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"個鼻托位整貼啲係咪可以頂住唔咁易跌?"},{"pid":"df77ff98012b4a9e0d3d08e16c85d52f67bc8e74","tid":2391744,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64e4b219